title: Age.of.Mythology.complete.v1.10.REPACK-vol1
description:
Age.of.Mythology.complete.v1.10.REPACK-vol1


Age of Mythology and the Titans expansion, patched to v1.10 and v1.03 (latest/final).

_Includes the golden gift campaign._ (DLC)

All 3 CDs, 2 patches, 2 serials, 2 cracks and 1 DLC in one package.


Launch the game in full HD with the "HD" shortcut, or modify the shortcut target for a different resolution.

(HD shortcut may only work from the second time you launch the game)
                                                  

                    
1. Mount or unpack .iso
2. Install
3. Install MSXML 4.0 if you don't have it yet ("msxml.msi" in the main game folder)
4. Play
